.el .ds Aq '
.TH oxillama 1  "oxillama 0.1.2" 
.SH NAME
oxillama \- Pure Rust LLM inference engine — the sovereign alternative to llama.cpp
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBoxillama\fR [\fB\-\-config\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Pure Rust LLM inference engine — the sovereign alternative to llama.cpp
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-config\fR \fI<PATH>\fR
Path to a TOML config file (overrides OXILLAMA_CONFIG env var)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
oxillama\-run(1)
Run inference on a GGUF model
.TP
oxillama\-serve(1)
Start the OpenAI\-compatible API server
.TP
oxillama\-info(1)
Print model information from a GGUF file
.TP
oxillama\-bench(1)
Run inference benchmarks
.TP
oxillama\-chat(1)
Interactive multi\-turn chat REPL
.TP
oxillama\-hub(1)
HuggingFace Hub operations (pull, list, rm)
.TP
oxillama\-completions(1)
Generate shell completion scripts
.TP
oxillama\-generate\-manpage(1)
Generate man pages for oxillama and write them to a directory
.TP
oxillama\-version(1)
Print verbose version information
.TP
oxillama\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH VERSION
v0.1.2
